32</td>\r\n<td>12U机箱，32X08/32X16/32X32 RGB/A矩阵切换器，插卡式；BNC/5Pin凤凰接口；<br />\r\n前面板按键/红外/RS-232控制/网络控制，字符液晶显示<a title=\"锚点： Audio矩阵\" name=\"A5\"></a></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>MUSE-RGB-4816/4832/4848/6416/6432/6448/6464</td>\r\n<td>五台级联4U机箱，48X16/48X32/48X48/64X16/64X32/64X48/64X64 RGB矩阵切换器，<br />\r\n插卡式；BNC/5Pin凤凰接口；前面板按键/红外/RS-232控制/网络控制，字符液晶显示</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr class=\"text-center\">\r\n<td class=\"alert alert-info\" colspan=\"2\">MUSE-A (Audio矩阵)</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>MUSE-A-1616</td>\r\n<td>2U机箱，16X16 纯音频矩阵切换器，插卡式；5Pin凤凰接口；<br />\r\n前面板按键/红外/RS-232控制/网络控制，字符液晶显示</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>MUSE-A-3216/3232</td>\r\n<td>4U机箱，32X16/32X32 纯音频矩阵切换器，插卡式；5Pin凤凰接口；<br />\r\n前面板按键/红外/RS-232控制/网络控制，字符液晶显示</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>MUSE-A-4816/4832/4848/6416/6432/6448/6464</td>\r\n<td>8U机箱，48X16/48X32/48X48/64X16/64X32/64X48/64X64 纯音频矩阵切换器，插卡式；<br />\r\n5Pin凤凰接口；前面板按键/红外/RS-232控制/网络控制，字符液晶显示</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</section>\r\n<div class=\"divider\"> </div>\r\n<section class=\"container\">\r\n<article class=\"row\">\r\n<div class=\"col-md-12 text-center\">\r\n<h3>系统拓扑图</h3>\r\n</div>\r\n</article>\r\n<article class=\"row\">\r\n<div class=\"col-md-12 text-center\"><img src=\"/wp-content/uploads/2016/07/Muse_tuopu.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"60%\" /></div>\r\n</article>\r\n</section>','DVI矩阵','','publish','closed','closed','','muse','','','2016-07-26 11:25:30','2016-07-26 03:25:30','',0,'http://chinargb.bin-go.cc/?post_type=product&#038;p=2855',0,'product','',0);
