	(2856,1,'2016-07-26 10:30:08','2016-07-26 02:30:08','<section class=\"container\">\n<article class=\"row\">\n<div class=\"col-md-7\">\n<h3>产品简介</h3>\n<p>TriF-T-R1SD-B是淳中科技自主研发的DVI光端机，满足用户对长距离、高清视频信号传输的需求。TriF-T-R1SD-B DVI光端机最高可支持1920×1200@60Hz的全高清分辨率，波长为1310nm，最远传输距离可达10km。 该产品采用专用ASIC和FPGA设计，实现了全数字无压缩，无失真的透明传输方式；本产品采用工业级的控制芯片，全表面贴装技术，和先进的开关电源，确保产品能在各种复杂的环境下高质量、无故障长期运行，是DVI信号远距离传输的理想之选。</p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"col-md-5\">\n[图片轮播 images=\"/wp-content/uploads/2016/07/TriFex_pro.jpg\"]\n</article>\n</section>\n<div class=\"divider\"> </div>\n<section class=\"container\">\n<article class=\"row\">\n<div class=\"col-md-12 text-center\">\n<h3>产品特点</h3>\n</div>\n</article>\n<div class=\"row\">\n<div class=\"col-md-3\">\n<div class=\"featured-box nobg border-only\">\n<div class=\"box-content\"><i class=\"fa fa-share-alt\"></i>\n<h4>传输距离</h4>\n<p>DVI视频信号远距离传输<br />\n最大传输距离达10km</p>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"col-md-3\">\n<div class=\"featured-box nobg border-only\"><i class=\"fa fa-delicious\"></i>\n<h4>最高分辨率</h4>\n<p>最高支持1920×1080@60Hz<br />\n分辨率全高清视频传输并向下兼容</p>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"col-md-3\">\n<div class=\"featured-box nobg border-only\"><i class=\"fa fa-openid\"></i>\n<h4>环通输出</h4>\n<p>发送器支持环路输出<br />\n便于本地视频信号显示</p>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"col-md-3\">\n<div class=\"featured-box nobg border-only\"><i class=\"fa fa-keyboard-o\"></i>\n<h4>按键设置</h4>\n<p>按键可以设置水平位置<br />\n垂直位置和采样相位</p>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</section>\n<div class=\"divider\"> </div>\n<section class=\"container\">\n<article class=\"row\">\n<div class=\"col-md-12 text-center\">\n<h3>技术参数</h3>\n</div>\n</article>\n<div class=\"table-responsive\">\n<table class=\"table table-bordered table-striped text-center\">\n<tbody>\n<tr class=\"text-center\">\n<td>发送端输入端口</td>\n<td>DVI-D信号输入×1</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>发送端环通接口</td>\n<td>DVI-D环通×1</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>接收端输出接口</td>\n<td>DVI-I信号（兼容VGA/DVI-D）×1</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>光接口</td>\n<td>单模 LC型</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>波长</td>\n<td>1310nm<