	(2920,1,'2016-07-26 11:27:51','2016-07-26 03:27:51','<section class=\"container\">\r\n<article class=\"row\">\r\n<div class=\"col-md-7\"><br />\r\n<br />\r\n<h3><strong>产品简介</strong></h3>\r\n<p>RGB长线驱动器主要用于解决在多媒体投影工程中，由于传输线缆距离过长或是质量不好及系统中其他设备造成的显示图象信号模糊、重影或拖尾等现象。在系统前端位置接入，即可明显改善或消除信号模糊、重影、拖尾等现象，最大限度的提高图象质量。对于75-2电缆，设备传输距离最大可达150米；对于75-3电缆，最大可达300米。</p>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"col-md-5\">\r\n[图片轮播 images=\"/wp-content/uploads/2016/07/RGB-105.png,/wp-content/uploads/2016/07/RGB-105-back.png,/wp-content/uploads/2016/07/RGB-105-front.png,/wp-content/uploads/2016/07/RGB-109-B.png,/wp-content/uploads/2016/07/RGB-109-Z.png\"]\r\n</div>\r\n</article>\r\n</section>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"divider\"><i class=\"fa fa-star\"></i></div>\r\n\r\n<section class=\"container\">\r\n<article class=\"row\">\r\n<div class=\"col-md-12 text-center\">\r\n<h3>产品特点</h3>\r\n</div>\r\n</article>\r\n<div class=\"row featured-box-minimal margin-bottom30 text-center\">\r\n<div class=\"col-md-4\">\r\n[servicebox title=\"信号格式\" icon=\"fa-file-image-o\"]\r\n支持RGBHV、RGBS、RGsB格式输入输出\r\n[/servicebox]\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"col-md-4\">\r\n[servicebox title=\"图像调节\" icon=\"fa-font\"]\r\n支持图像水平、垂直中心调节\r\n[/servicebox]\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"col-md-4\">\r\n[servicebox title=\"增益调节\" icon=\"fa-signal\"]\r\n支持多档位输出增益调节\r\n[/servicebox]\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"row featured-box-minimal margin-bottom30 text-center\">\r\n<div class=\"col-md-4\">\r\n[servicebox title=\"同步显示\" icon=\"fa-css3\"]\r\n行、场同步信号频率显示\r\n[/servicebox]\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"col-md-4\">\r\n[servicebox title=\"环通输出\" icon=\"fa-arrows-alt\"]\r\n支持环通输出，连接本地监视器\r\n[/servicebox]\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"col-md-4\">\r\n[servicebox title=\"音频传输\" icon=\"fa-delicious\"]\r\n计算机音频到平衡音频的有源驱动器\r\n[/servicebox]\r\n</div>\r\n</section>\r\n<div class=\"divider\"><i class=\"fa fa-star\"></i></div>\r\n<section class=\"container\">\r\n<article class=\"row\">\r\n<div class=\"col-md-12 text-center\">\r\n<h3>产品资料下载</h3>\r\n</div>\r\n</articl