	(2922,1,'2016-07-26 11:28:17','2016-07-26 03:28:17','<section class=\"container\">\r\n<article class=\"row\">\r\n<div class=\"col-md-7\">\r\n<h3>产品简介</h3>\r\n<p>DVI-103是淳中科技自主研发的双绞线传输器，其可以将DVI视频信号转换为HDBaseT信号，进而通过六类双绞线远距离传输，最大传输距离为100m（1920×1200@60Hz），是DVI高清数字视频信号远距离传输的理想之选，同时可以配合淳中其他音视频处理设备使用。</p>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"col-md-5\">\r\n[图片轮播 images=\"/wp-content/uploads/2016/07/dvi103_pro1.png,/wp-content/uploads/2016/07/dvi103_pro2.png\"]\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"owl-item\">\r\n<div><img class=\"img-responsive\" src=\"/wp-content/uploads/2016/07/dvi103_pro2.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"555\" height=\"311\" /></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"owl-controls clickable\"> </div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</article>\r\n</section>\r\n<div class=\"divider\"> </div>\r\n<section class=\"container\">\r\n<article class=\"row\">\r\n<div class=\"col-md-12 text-center\">\r\n<h3>型号分类</h3>\r\n<p>DVI-103有2个型号，其主要功能和区别如下：</p>\r\n</div>\r\n</article>\r\n<div class=\"table-responsive\">\r\n<table class=\"table table-bordered table-striped text-center\">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr class=\"text-center\">\r\n<td rowspan=\"4\">DVI-103</td>\r\n<td rowspan=\"2\">DVI-103-100</td>\r\n<td>DVI-103-100-TX发送端</td>\r\n<td rowspan=\"2\">最大传输距离为100m</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr class=\"text-center\">\r\n<td>DVI-103-100-RX接收端</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr class=\"text-center\">\r\n<td rowspan=\"2\">DVI-103-70</td>\r\n<td>DVI-103-70-TX发送端</td>\r\n<td rowspan=\"2\">最大传输距离为70m</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr class=\"text-center\">\r\n<td>DVI-103-70-RX接收端</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</section>\r\n<div class=\"divider\"> </div>\r\n<section class=\"container\">\r\n<article class=\"row\">\r\n<div class=\"col-md-12 text-center\">\r\n<h3>产品特点</h3>\r\n</div>\r\n</article>\r\n<div class=\"row\">\r\n<div class=\"col-md-4\">\r\n[servicebox2 title=\"传输距离\" icon=\"fa-share-alt\"]\r\n单台最大支持100m无损传输<br />\r\n支持级联，最多延长至1km\r\n[/servicebox2]\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"col-md-4\">\r\n[servicebox2 title=\"最高分辨率\" icon